Package: examstats
Title: What the Package Does (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Logan", "Kelly", , "logan.kelly@uwrf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5938-979X"))
Description: `examstats` is an R package for educators, students, and stats enthusiasts to simulate data and craft diverse quiz and exam questions. It generates data for common distributions, offers tools for manipulation and analysis, and creates multiple-choice, short-answer, and descriptive questions from simulated data.
